snippet.title: Unfiltered Ep 2- Johnny Depp is THE VICTIM  HERE #JusticeForJohnnyDepp
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp is the true victim here
 today on unfiltered I speak on me Johnny Depp and Amber Heard ongoing Court battle and feud between the two I also talked about how Johnny Depp has been repeatedly blackballed in Hollywood for the past seven years and how I feel it is completely wrong given me obscene amount of evidence against Amber Heard to prove her guilt.  Amber Heard was in fact the aggressor here.
She has gone to great lengths to try and ruin Johnny Depp's life, career,  and was pretty successful  Disney dropped him, Warner Bros dropped him he is lost multiple opportunities given these false allegations and  it's completely wrong.
Given the amount of evidence that proves Amber Heard guilt I have no fucking  idea how she still has supporters

Look at the bigger picture 
#JusticeForJohnnyDepp #JohnnyDepp
